name: android-gradle-best-practices.mdc
description: Best practices for dependency management and Gradle in Android
globs: **/*.gradle.kts

- Use version catalog for dependency management
- Centralize dependencies in a single file
- Use buildSrc or Gradle Kotlin DSL
- Implement proper Gradle configurations
- Use Gradle build flavors for different environments
- Optimize build time with Gradle configuration cache
- Use dynamic feature modules for large apps
- Implement proper ProGuard rules
- Use proper versioning strategy
- Avoid dependency conflicts
- Keep dependencies up-to-date
- Implement proper CI/CD integration 